Title: Susan Strong
Writer: Mark Banker (story), Patrick McHale (story), Adam Muto, Kent Osborne (story), Rebecca Sugar, Pendleton Ward (story)
Actors: Jeremy Shada, John DiMaggio, Hynden Walch, Tom Kenny
Plot: Having always believed he is the only human left in the Land of Ooo, Finn believes he has discovered a tribe to primitive humans living underground.
